According to the command monitoring spec:
bq. All legacy operations MUST be converted to their equivalent commands in the 3.2 server in the event's command and reply fields. This includes OP_INSERT, OP_DELETE, OP_UPDATE, OP_QUERY, OP_GET_MORE and OP_KILL_CURSORS.
