The Mongos SRV Poller (SrvMonitor) shouldn't start until 60 seconds after the client is first created as discussed in HELP-36687:
{quote}
bq. Yes, however, what confuses me is that it all happens within a couple of seconds since the MongoClient was instantiated since the added endpoints were removed. I thought the driver won't be querying the DNS faster than 1 every 60 seconds.

